sequenceDiagram
    participant R as Requester
    participant N as Network
    participant P as Provider
    participant E as Escrow

    R->>N: JobRequest<br/>(model, prompt, budget)
    N->>P: Broadcast Request

    P->>N: JobBid<br/>(price, latency, reputation)
    N->>R: Collect Bids

    R->>E: Lock Funds
    R->>N: BidAccepted<br/>(winner_peer_id)
    N->>P: Notify Winner

    P->>P: Execute Job
    P->>N: JobResult<br/>(output)
    N->>R: Deliver Result

    R->>R: Verify Result
    R->>E: Release Funds
    E->>P: Payment
